Class TripleOfIntsString

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cloud9.io.triple.TripleOfIntsString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TripleOfIntsString>, Writable, WritableComparable<TripleOfIntsString>

    public class TripleOfIntsString
extends Object
implements WritableComparable<TripleOfIntsString>

    WritableComparable representing a pair of integers. The elements in the pair are referred to as the left and right elements. The natural sort order is: first by the left element, and then by the right element.
